description: The full key identifier, attributes, and tags are provided in the response. This operation requires the keys/list permission.

maxresults.description: Maximum number of results to return in a page. If not specified the service will return up to 25 results.

nextlink.description: The URL to get the next set of keys.

value.description: A response message containing a list of keys in the key vault along with a link to the next page of keys.
